- `RiemannSum f a b n = ∑_{i=0}^{n-1} f(a + (i+1)(b-a)/n) * (b-a)/n`

The difference is:
`|∑_{i=0}^{n*k-1} f(a + (i+1)(b-a)/(n*k)) * (b-a)/(n*k) - ∑_{i=0}^{n-1} f(a + (i+1)(b-a)/n) * (b-a)/n|`

